entries.title_d: Capture a dangerous fugitive in the Naboo System
entries.title: Naboo System: Capture the Ay'Nat Captain's personal yacht
entries.thanks_5: Thanks for getting us out of there.
entries.thanks_4: Thanks for getting us out of there.
entries.thanks_3: Thanks for getting us out of there.
entries.thanks_2: Try to keep this gem in perfect condition.
entries.taunt_5: You have something that belongs to us.
entries.taunt_4: You have something that belongs to us.

entries.taunt_1: You have something that belongs to us.
entries.target_disabled: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#00ff00 The Ay'Nat Captain's ship has been disabled. Capture operation will begin shortly. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.recovery_success: The pirate Captain's yacht has been secured. Good job, pilot.
entries.quest_recover_d: Pull up close to begin the capture process.
entries.quest_escort_d: Escort the craft safely out of the Naboo System
entries.quest_disable_d: Attack this ships engines to disable.
entries.panic_2: Keep the heat off, we can't take much.
entries.failed_escape: The Ay'Nat Captain's yacht has escaped the area. This is a disgrace! Return to base at once!
entries.failed_destroy: The Ay'Nat Captain's yacht was destroyed! This is unacceptable! Return to base at once. You are to blame for this failure!
entries.escort_wiped_out: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#00ff00 The pirate captain's escort has been eliminated. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.escort_remaining: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#00ff00 %DI ships remain in the pirate captain's escort. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.complete: We've made it to safety. Jumping to lightspeed...now.
entries.capture_started: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#00ff00 Primary mission target capture operation underway. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.capture_phase_2: Resistance eliminated. We've taken the bridge. We'll be underway shortly.
entries.capture_phase_1: Boarding party is facing light resistance.
entries.capture_complete: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Primary mission target capture operation complete! \#pcontrast3  >
entries.attack_stopped: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Enemy activity has stopped. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.attack_notify: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Enemy craft detected on attack vector. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.arrival_phase_2: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 The Ay'Nat Captain's yacht has arrived. Disable the yacht and eliminate her escort! \#pcontrast3 >

entries.abort: Roger, abort code received. Heading home...
